      "width": 560,
      "height": 260,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Data / Schema Library\n\nThis package models structural schema concepts without swallowing full ETL or validation engines.\n\nV1 classes:\n- `entity`\n- `field`\n- `relation`\n- `constraint`\n- `enum`\n- `mapping`\n\nDeferred:\n- `validation-rule`\n- `transform`\n- `source`\n- `schema-note`",
